  "texts": [
    "As networks grow in size and complexity, the computational demands of AI models increase.",
    "Techniques like PCA and Autoencoders are frequently employed for dimensionality reduction, making it feasible to analyze largescale data streams efficiently.",
    "These methods reduce the complexity of the data by focusing on the most significant features, allowing real-time detection of anomalies without overwhelming computational resources.",
    "However, scalability often comes at the cost of accuracy.",
    "Deep Learning models, while powerful, can struggle with the vast data generated by telecom networks if not properly optimized."
  ],
